name: Shell Gadus S1 OG 150
description: Open Gear and Wire Rope Grease

localDocs.name: Gadus S1 OG 150 United States EN 140002686046 EHS V1.2 12-JAN-2017

marketing: Shell Gadus S1 OG are a range of high viscosity, residual-type (bituminous) lubricants, which are recommended principally for open gears, sugar mills and wire rope applications which require an adhesive, high load-carrying, EP product. All grades are blends of bitumen and heavy mineral based oils, blended in different proportions to suit various applications.
